OL,3,C'My mother lay on the cold road dying'
OL,4,CSon's anger as driver is jailed for
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FThe family of a woman who was hit and
OL,8,Fkilled by an HGV which had driven
OL,9,Fthrough a red light on a pedestrian
OL,10,Fcrossing in Oxfordshire, have revealed
OL,11,Fthe driver didn't call an ambulance or
OL,12,Ftry to get help, as she lay dying in
OL,13,Fthe road.
OL,15,FPedestrian Patricia Grace was crossing
OL,16,FOxford Road in Kidlington, in October
OL,17,F2022, when she was struck by a lorry
OL,18,Fbeing driven by Dariusz Meczynski.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/16
