OL,3,C'My mother lay on the cold road dying'
OL,4,CSon's anger as driver is jailed for
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FMeczynski, aged 51, of no fixed abode
OL,8,Fwas jailed for three years and nine
OL,9,Fmonths at Oxford Crown Court on 9
OL,10,FDecember this year.
OL,12,FAs part of a tribute released on
OL,13,Fsentencing, Patricia's son and wider
OL,14,Ffamily accused Dariusz Meczynski of
OL,15,Ftrying to "minimize his involvement to
OL,16,Favoid justice."
