OL,4,CSon's anger as driver is jailed for
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,F"My mother left home on that Thursday
OL,8,Fmorning to go volunteer cleaning at
OL,9,Fher local catholic church. An act of
OL,10,Fkindness that she had done every
OL,11,FThursday morning for as long as anyone
OL,12,Fcan remember. As we know she was not
OL,13,Fto arrive that day due to the
OL,14,Fcriminally dangerous driving of
OL,15,FMeczynski.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/16
