PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F414A1735227313
OL,3,C'My mother lay on the cold road dying'
OL,4,CSon's anger as driver is jailed for
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,F"She did not deserve to lose her life
OL,8,Fthat morning, she was simply using a
OL,9,Fpedestrian crossing that was on green
OL,10,Ffor her. Mum was a very cautious
OL,11,Findividual, and the green cross code
OL,12,Fwas drummed into us as children, she
OL,13,Fhad every right to use that crossing
OL,14,Fand should have been safe to do so. We
OL,15,Fdon't know why Meczynski did not see
OL,16,Fher but it is clear that he must have
OL,17,Fbeen woefully distracted for a
OL,18,Fprolonged period as he approached the
OL,19,Fpedestrian crossing that was on red
OL,20,Ffor traffic.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
