PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F414A1735227313
OL,3,C'My mother lay on the cold road dying'
OL,4,CSon's anger as driver is jailed for
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,F"In the immediate aftermath of the
OL,8,Fincident, while my mother lay on the
OL,9,Fcold road dying, Meczynski did not get
OL,10,Fout of his cab. He did not try to help
OL,11,For even call for an ambulance.
OL,12,FInstead, he phoned his boss. This is a
OL,13,Fhuge aggravating factor for the family
OL,14,Fand is just the first instance of his
OL,15,Fdeliberate attempts to try and
OL,16,Fminimize his involvement to avoid
OL,17,Fjustice.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/16
