OL,4,CSon's anger as driver is jailed for
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,F"When the police arrived later that
OL,8,Fmorning at my father's house, the
OL,9,Ffamily home that he shared with his
OL,10,Fdearly loved wife of 51 years, they
OL,11,Fwere carrying my mother's bag, they
OL,12,Ftried her key in the door and at first
OL,13,Fhe thanked them for their time and
OL,14,Fthought they were returning lost
OL,15,Fproperty. When they explained the
OL,16,Freason for the visit, his life
OL,17,Fdevastatingly changed forever.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/16
