OL,3,C'My mother lay on the cold road dying'
OL,4,CSon's anger as driver is jailed for
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,F"As the accident happened so close to
OL,8,Fhome, this is a constant reminder,
OL,9,Fespecially when he has to use the
OL,10,Fcrossing, which he must do regularly,
OL,11,Fto visit his sister or the local shop.
OL,12,FHe is now very lonely and struggles to
OL,13,Fstay in the house as everything is a
OL,14,Freminder of mum and what has been
OL,15,Ftaken from him.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/16
