OL,3,C'My mother lay on the cold road dying'
OL,4,CSon's anger as driver is jailed for
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,F"Of course, many people who knew Mum
OL,8,Fhave been affected by this incident.
OL,9,FShe had just one sister, my Aunty Jean
OL,10,Fwho misses the telephone calls and
OL,11,Fregular visits for catch-ups and
OL,12,Fsupport. My father's sister Carol lost
OL,13,Fher best friend and confident. My
OL,14,Fmother was well known and loved in the
OL,15,Flocal community for her volunteer
OL,16,Fwork, helping neighbors or simply
OL,17,Fbeing remembered as 'that nice lady,
OL,18,Fthat worked in the local pharmacy'.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/16
