OL,3,C'My mother lay on the cold road dying'
OL,4,CSon's anger as driver is jailed for
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,F"When this tragic event occurred I had
OL,8,Frecently started my degree to become a
OL,9,Fqualified paramedic. I am still on the
OL,10,Fcourse, but my grades have suffered as
OL,11,Fa direct result of the stress, and
OL,12,Fsleepless nights this has put upon me.
OL,14,F"The incident itself is bad enough and
OL,15,Fhas had devastating consequences to us
OL,16,Fas a family but deep down we as a
OL,17,Ffamily understand that this was an
OL,18,Faccident.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/16
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
