OL,3,C'My mother lay on the cold road dying'
OL,4,CSon's anger as driver is jailed for
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,F"We don't for a second believe that
OL,8,FMeczynski woke up that morning with
OL,9,Fthe intention of hurting anyone.
OL,10,FHowever, it is also painfully clear to
OL,11,Fus as a family that Meczynski has done
OL,12,Feverything he can to avoid justice,
OL,13,Fcowardly fleeing the country to avoid
OL,14,Ffacing the consequences of his actions.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G13/16
