OL,4,CSon's anger as driver is jailed for
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,F"This has meant that the case has
OL,8,Fdragged on for nearly two years. Two
OL,9,Fyears of dealing with the police,
OL,10,Fcourts and CPS, furthermore
OL,11,Fcompounding our grief whilst Meczynski
OL,12,Fhas been driving his lorry around
OL,13,FEurope living his life whilst ours is
OL,14,Fin tatters."
