OL,7,FLead investigator Richard Thorpe, of
OL,8,Fthe Serious Collision Investigation
OL,9,FUnit, said: "Tragically, as a direct
OL,10,Fresult of Meczynski's driving, he
OL,11,Ffailed to stop at a red traffic light
OL,12,Fand collided with the victim resulting
OL,13,Fin her death.
OL,15,F"My thoughts and the thoughts of all
OL,16,Fof us remain with the victim's family
OL,17,Fand friends who have shown great
OL,18,Fdignity and patience while we brought
OL,19,Fthis case to court.
